541
00:49:27,884 --> 00:49:42,212
[SPEAKER_05]: There may be others, but the only one I know of that does combine wards, and I think we've discussed in past meetings that Lowell switched to ward representation for both city council and school committee based on a Voting Rights Act lawsuit as part of a settlement.

542
00:49:43,968 --> 00:49:52,854
[SPEAKER_05]: They landed with eight ward city councilors and three at large, but their school committee has seven members.

543
00:49:53,054 --> 00:49:56,096
[SPEAKER_05]: What they did for their school committee was they combined wards.

544
00:49:56,777 --> 00:50:11,748
